claim.claim-text:
4. A method of storing, of securing for travel, and for transporting omnium-gatherum, including the steps of 
(a) providing the apparatus of claim 1; 
(b) placing said body in said deployed position; 
(c) telescopically extending said first member to said first operative position; 
(d) placing omnium-gatherum in said container; 
(e) using said apparatus such that said wheels roll over the ground a selected distance; 
(f) placing said first member in said second operative position; 
(g) folding said body to said stowed operative position; 
(h) carrying said apparatus a selected distance; and, 
(i) removing at least some of said omnium-gatherum from said container.
